author: Techlore
description:
Can a laptop offer privacy & security without compromises? NovaCustom claims to, with QubesOS/Linux support, customizability, disabling Intel ME, and coreboot as its notable features. But I'll be breaking down what I like & dislike about the NovaCustom V56 to help you decide if it's for you.

Thank you to our sponsor Notesnook! They offer E2EE notes in an open source ecosystem, free to try. Visit their site to get started: https://notesnook.com
